            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">About the Book Notes Web Application</h1>
            <p class="col-md-8 fs-4">Book Notes is a user-friendly web application that allows you to catalog and manage the books you've read. It's a space to record important details about each book, including titles, authors, ratings, and personal notes.</p>
