            <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-body-tertiary border rounded-3">
              <h2>Technologies and Functionalites</h2>
              <p>This web application is built using Express.js for the server framework, PostgreSQL for database management, and EJS for rendering dynamic web pages. The app facilitates the management of a book collection, allowing users to add, edit, and delete book entries. Body-parser middleware handles form data, while Express.static serves static assets like CSS and JavaScript. The application includes a search feature for quick book look-ups. With API Integration, Axios is used to fetch book cover images from the Open Library API based on ISBNs. The dotenv package keeps environment variables secure.</p>
